Please answer the question.

00:20:32.745 --> 00:20:34.730
In any case, you will be fine.

00:20:34.774 --> 00:20:36.569
Please don't run from your destiny.

00:20:36.569 --> 00:20:38.980
I will not run from my destiny.

00:20:55.272 --> 00:20:56.861
I can't.

00:20:57.066 --> 00:20:59.917
As a fan, how can I possibly be his secretary?

00:20:59.917 --> 00:21:01.917
(Transfer Request Form)
I'll confess to the section chief tomorrow.

00:21:01.917 --> 00:21:06.860
Loving your fave means supporting them from a distance.

00:21:07.168 --> 00:21:08.743
That's the right way.

00:21:09.613 --> 00:21:11.134
