00:21:24.628 --> 00:21:26.457
but I have made my decision.

00:21:26.486 --> 00:21:30.912
As I said at the press conference, once I finish my current work...

00:21:31.083 --> 00:21:33.654
I will be going on an indefinite hiatus.

00:21:34.338 --> 00:21:37.745
There may not be a farewell event.

00:21:38.059 --> 00:21:40.537
I feel very sorry about that.

00:21:42.361 --> 00:21:44.618
My days as an actor...

00:21:45.207 --> 00:21:49.573
thanks to all of you, were an incredibly precious...

00:21:49.833 --> 00:21:51.833
and happy time for me.

00:21:53.532 --> 00:21:55.532
Thank you all so much.

00:22:06.430 --> 00:22:07.891
